{"tid":30030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲仔中援交陷阱 被呃3萬蚊買點數卡","createTime":"2016-12-09T03:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T03:15:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf85ca8f40671c3665121af37ef0f2f18acb4fb","tid":30030,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"昨晚約9時07分，一名17歲姓陳青年，在旺角山東街近洗衣街報警，聲稱較早前透過手機應用程式認識一名女子，她聲稱可以提供援交服務。<br />\n<br />\n其後該女子及一名男子，分別致電事主，要求他購買點數卡。他按指示共購買總值約3萬元的點數卡後懷疑被騙，於是報案。案件由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56022631&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56022631%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161209&d=4CU04Cls7y1y4H5xr4VM4EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ac14eb23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56022631%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161209&h=eb6439ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56022631&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161209</a>"},{"pid":"964f9eb8b2cbd01726f29eb193ea2b3c90477cc3","tid":30030,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae026ea4a31479cf22bbe29bf720af9c00d86e89","tid":30030,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:12:18.000Z","msg":"3萬蚊點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 17歲"},{"pid":"ce1873c446bbe48cd25f4ee39bd9a9891018d610","tid":30030,"uid":35923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"17歲有3萭俾人呃都幾勁"},{"pid":"74c4ebde9b49270537b662deb5a6a7ea4ba42956","tid":30030,